---

import "../styles/style.css";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import TopBar from "../components/TopBar__EN.astro";
import PicHeader from "../components/Pics/PicHeader.astro";
import Reviews from "../components/Reviews.astro"
import ItiItem from "../layouts/ItiItem.astro";
import Footer from "../components/footer__EN.astro";
import IFY from "../assets/images/footer/Iceland-for-You-logo.webp"
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Private tours in Iceland | Lilja Tours - Icelandic Travel Agency</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <TopBar linkfr="/fr/"></TopBar>
        <div class="headerContainerPic">
            <PicHeader srcMobile="/pictures/homepage/headers/volcano-love.webp" srcPC="/pictures/homepage/headers/waterfall-love.webp" alt="Picture of stunning icelandic landscapes, waterfalls and volcnaoes" title="Lilja Tours travel agency"></PicHeader></div>
            <div class="headerGradient"></div>
            <div class="headerInfos">
                <h1>The Icelandic Expert for Your Private Tours</h1>
                <h2>Tailored travels with personal driver-guide</h2>                
            </div>
        </div>

    </header>
    <main>

        <Reviews/>

        <section>
        <ItiItem    
        srcMobile="/pictures/homepage/why-private-mobile.webp",
        itiItemPicSrcPC="/pictures/homepage/why-private-pc.webp",
        itiItemPicAlt="Wonderful landscapes from Iceland",
        itiItemPicTitle="Travel with a private tour",
        itiItemTitle="Why choose a private Tour?">
        <p>A private tour combines the in-depth knowledge and comfort of a guided experience with the flexibility of a self-guided journey. With a private, tailor-made tour, you remain in control while our dedicated guides ensure that your trip is nothing short of exceptional.</p>

            <p>Together, we create a customized itinerary that covers everything from transportation to accommodation. We provide suggestions, but the final decisions are always yours.</p>
            
            <p>For day tours, we offer a wide selection of ready-to-book options available directly on our website. Each of these tours is fully customizable, so don’t hesitate to reach out if you’d like to make any modifications.</p>
            
           <!-- <p>If you’re traveling independently, we also have a dedicated section for you. There, you’ll find a curated list of excursions across Iceland. We’ve carefully selected trusted partners who provide top-quality services throughout the country.
            </p> -->
    </ItiItem>
</section>
<section>
    <ItiItem    
    srcMobile="/pictures/homepage/ify-mobile.webp",
    itiItemPicSrcPC="/pictures/homepage/ify-pc.webp",
    itiItemPicAlt="Wonderful landscapes from Iceland",
    itiItemPicTitle="Travel with a private tour",
    itiItemTitle="Discover Iceland For You. Our premium brand for luxury group travels">
    <p>At the beginning of 2025, we introduced a new brand dedicated to high-end multiday group tours. Our meticulously designed itineraries allow you to experience Iceland in top-tier hotels, with the most comfortable vehicles, and with the same exceptional level of service that <strong>Lilja Tours</strong> has been delivering since 2021—all at a more affordable price than a private tour.</p> 
    <p>For 2025, we have scheduled three departures (4 to 12 participants maximum):</p> 
    <ul> 
        <li><a>10-day Luxury Ring Road Tour in September</a></li> 
        <li><a>5-day Adventure Tour in October</a></li> 
        <li><a>5-day Discovery Tour in November</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="https://www.iceland-for-you.com" title="See our group tours offer"><Image src={IFY} alt="Iceland for you Logo" width="596" height="426" class="logos" loading="lazy"></Image></a>

</ItiItem>
</section>

        
    </main>
    <Footer/>
</body>
</html>
<style>

    ul {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: white;
        list-style-position: inside;
        font-weight: lighter;
    }

    .logos {
        max-width: 50%;
        height: auto;
        display: flex;
        margin-inline: auto;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
    }
 .header {
            min-height: 100dvh;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .headerContainerPic {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: calc(100dvh - 3.5rem);
            max-height: calc(100dvh - 3.5rem);
            position: relative;
        }

        .headerGradient {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: calc(100dvh - 3.5rem);
            max-height: calc(100dvh - 3.5rem);
            position: absolute;
            top: 3.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.00) 99.06%);
        }

        .headerInfos {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 3.5rem 0 0 0;
            display: flex;
            height:  calc(100dvh - 3.5rem);
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            align-content: center;
            gap: 5rem;

        }

        h1 {
        color: #FFF;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, calc(5vw + 1rem), 4rem );
        font-weight: lighter;
        min-width: min-content;
        max-width: max-content;
        text-wrap: balance;
        animation-name: Title;
        animation-duration: 2s;
        animation-fill-mode: forwards;
        opacity: 0;
    }

    h2 {
        color: #FFF;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, calc(5vw + 1rem), 2.5rem );
        font-weight: lighter;
        min-width: min-content;
        max-width: max-content;
        text-wrap: balance;
        animation-name: Title;
        animation-duration: 2s;
        animation-delay: 1s;
        animation-fill-mode: forwards;
        opacity: 0;
        font-style: italic;
    }



@keyframes Title {
    from {opacity: 0}
    to {opacity: 1}
}

@media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    main h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, calc(1vw + 1rem), 2rem );
    }

    main p {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }


}

</style>



